			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Scottnearing.jpg" class="image" title="Scott Nearing, 1916"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a6/Scottnearing.jpg/180px-Scottnearing.jpg" width="180" height="243" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Scottnearing.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Scott Nearing, 1916</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Scott Nearing</b> (1883—1983) was an <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a> <a href="/wiki/Radical" title="Radical">radical</a> <a href="/wiki/Economics" title="Economics">economist</a>, <a href="/wiki/Educator" title="Educator" class="mw-redirect">educator</a>, <a href="/wiki/Writer" title="Writer">writer</a>, <a href="/wiki/Political_activism" title="Political activism" class="mw-redirect">political activist</a>, and advocate of <a href="/wiki/Simple_living" title="Simple living">simple living</a>.</p>
